# Firebase iOS client config (GoogleService-Info.plist) is committed: it's not a
# secret — it ships inside every app binary and its api_key/app_id are project
# identifiers restricted by bundle-id + Firebase rules (matches Android's tracked
# google-services.json). The Firebase ADMIN service account stays in env only.

